This folder contains in general 4 different types of files i.e. 
*	manual created source files
		-	testlib.i
		-	testlib.cpp
*	generated files
		-	testlib.o
		-	testlib.py
		-	testlib.pyc
		-	_testlib.so
		-	testlib_wrap.cxx
		-	testlib_wrap.o
*	script to generate files
		-	code
*	script to test functionalities of the created library
		-	testit.py

How to use:
	./code testlib
	./testit.py
